title: Tshedimošo ya Setegeniki - Tempele ya Orbital
heading: Tshedimošo ya Sethekniki

satellite.heading: Sathalaete
satellite.specs:
Ditekanyo: 50x58x64 mm
1P PocketQube ya go swana le
Boima ba 'mele: 245 gr
Didirišwa: aluminiamo, gauta, fiberglass, le dikarolo tša elektroniki.
Orbit: Bophahamo ba 525 ± 25 km SE; sekame: SSO 97.6 ± 0.1 °
Sethuthupi: PSLV (Polar Satellite Launch Vehicle) yeo e šomišwago ke ISRO

antenna.heading: Antena/Sebopego sa go betlwa
antenna.specs:
Ditekanyo: 6 m (bophara) e 1.2m (bophahamo)
Boima: 46 kg
Didirišwa: aluminiamo, epoxy seiponeng boto, gauta aluminium dome e fegilwego ka sebopego sa scaffolding.

radio.heading: Ditlhalošo tša Radio
radio.specs:
Kgokagano ya go theoga: 468.5 MHz
Modulation: CSS
Bandwidth: TBD
